        "id": "hindi-modern-sumitranandan-pant-madhushala-ki-raah",
        "title": "Madhushala ki Raah",
        "poet": "सुमित्रानंदन पंत / Sumitranandan Pant",
        "poet_dates": "1900 - 1977",
        "poet_bio": "The creative journey of Sumitranandan Pant represents a deep meditation on nature, love, and the complex mysteries of existence. Active during the modern transition, they combined rigorous classical training with a modern awareness of personal alienation. Their published collections stand as milestones of the hindi literary canon, celebrated for their exquisite imagery, musical rhythm, and ability to give shape to the unspeakable aspects of human feeling.",
