        "poet_dates": "1911 - 1987",
        "poet_bio": "Sachchidananda Agyeya was a major voice in hindi literature during the modern period. Their work is widely recognized for its deep emotional impact, philosophical insights, and innovative structure. Over several decades of active writing and creative exploration, they developed a unique style that blended traditional meters with personal reflections, capturing the collective spirit of their generation and earning a permanent place in the hearts of readers worldwide.",
