          "era": "classical",
          "meaning": "This celebrated poem by Abdul Rahim Khan-i-Khana explores the delicate boundaries of memory, consciousness, and emotion, reflecting on how quiet moments of observation reveal profound spiritual truths about our shared human journey.",
          "resonance_words": [
            "puzzling",
            "clarifying",
            "aching"
          ],
          "title_hi": "नीर भरी दुख की बदली",
          "text_devanagari": "मैं नीर भरी दुख की बदली!\nस्पंदन में चिर निस्पंद बसा,\nक्रंदन में आहत विश्व हंसा,\nनयनों में दीपक से जलते, पलकों में निर्झरिणी मचली!",
          "text_roman": "Main neer bhari dukh ki badli!\nSpandan mein chir nispand basa,\nKrandan mein aahat vishwa hansa,\nNayanon mein deepak se jalte, palkon mein nirjharini machli!"
